    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c817c126c4990b5820195b0"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Yes, Yang, there are no other mercenary units available than the [[DM.Factions[faction_GhostRiders],Ghost Riders]], who have been already fighting with the Restoration and were responsible for the liberation of the 'Ice Box' at [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreWeldry],Weldry]] and the initial capture of my cousin Victoria.\n\nThey're a solid outfit but they were ambushed by the Directorate at [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreKatinka],Katinka]] and took heavy losses during that debacle.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 3,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c00e5d78b5a0a4d8c9bfff2"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "5a6aa41a623035a020000e2a",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c31baffee4f0abc509cfa65"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "I have also received word from my [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAranoRoyalGuard],Royal Guard]] members that I dismissed after [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreDiik],Diik]] and the first ambush by [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreGrayNoton],Gray Noton]].\n\nWith them, and both mercenary units I should be able to bring at least a company of 'Mechs to the rally point.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "Will that be enough, Lady Arano?",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 4,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c8b06f288080f4fe2781799"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "5a6aa41a623035a020000e2a",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c78efa5e80986c4eed9ce8e"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "We'll worry about that in the future, Commander {COMMANDER.LastName}.\n\nThe [[DM.Factions[faction_AuriganRestoration],Restoration]] is rather shaky at the moment with the losses they suffered at the hands of Lord Espinosa's forces and the [[DM.Factions[faction_TaurianConcordat],Taurians]].",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 5,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cb641e70b9cb420d62d2421"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "5a6aa41a623035a020000e2a",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c9462e88adec09e0f3ce162"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "And the Magistracy hasn't provided any actual support rather than diplomatic announcements because they don't want to be dragged into a Periphery conflict while the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreInnerSphere],Inner Sphere]] is going through a new succession war.\n\nEven independent worlds are reluctant to provide help to the Restoration.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 6,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c521a2a60e20152b2f11c63"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cab171c25735b59df6cd03e"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Which bring us to this planet, where after leaving the Restoration's service, the Ghost Riders found work in one of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreCapellanMarches],Capellan Marches]]' worlds.\n\nThey were defending a mining operation in one of [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreCygnus],Cygnus]]' moons, which also allowed them to also hide from any Directorate reprisals.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 7,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c41f86f83f9be9cbcf8b8a5"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "5a6aa41a623035a020000e2a",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c6ff5dafa919f0c964f1b25"
      },
      "index": 7,
      "text": "They are willing to serve me but after their betrayal at Katinka they are very suspicious of anyone in the initial Restoration.\n\nEven your company is seen as questionable by them, which considering the our recent events isn't that unreasonable.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "And since Lady Arano can't be here, I'll need to step in for you.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 8,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c21e213dc974b63607c6715"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
