    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cdf4dbbc53ae5d44f5993d9"
      },
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Sumire, they mostly disagreed with their former CO's decision of running away after Katinka, after they saw plenty of the Taurian atrocities that are taking place in the Reach.\n\nAfter I announced my birthright during the games at [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHardcore],Hardcore]], the Riders' XO, Captain Johnson, challenged him and killed him in a duel.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 12,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
