      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cda7cccaf71aafed08eb4e6"
      },
      "index": 13,
      "text": "I also agree with you, Yang.\n\nThat's why I'm ordering the company to rescue the Ghost Riders before you recover the <i>Argo</i>.",
